+# Software Test Description (STD)
+
+## Feature: VM Snapshot Restore with runStrategy RerunOnFailure
+
+**STP Reference:** [CNV-63819](https://issues.redhat.com/browse/CNV-63819)
+**Jira ID:** CNV-63819
+**Generated:** 2026-02-22
+
+---
+
+## Summary
+
+This STD covers test scenarios for verifying that VM snapshot restore completes successfully when the VM uses `runStrategy: RerunOnFailure`. The fix addresses a bug where `virt-controller` would immediately attempt to start the VM during a restore operation, preventing the restore from completing. Tests verify the core fix, post-restore VM lifecycle, regression across other run strategies, data integrity after restore, and multiple restore operations.
+
+---
+
+## Test Files
+
+### File: `tests/storage/snapshots/test_snapshot_restore_run_strategy.py`
+
